    {
      "id": 4000,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🚨 Threat: Ransomware & DGA (Domain Generation Algorithms)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 81, "w": 24, "h": 1}
    },
    {
      "id": 40001,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 82, "w": 24, "h": 3},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**How to read this section:** Domain Generation Algorithms (DGAs) are used by ransomware and botnets to randomly guess thousands of gibberish domains (e.g., `xkqztp.ru`) to find a live command server.\n* 🟢 **Normal:** NXDOMAIN (failed lookup) ratios hover below 10%. New domains occasionally bump up when visiting new websites.\n* 🔴 **Abnormal / Threat:** A massive, simultaneous vertical spike in 'New Domains' and the 'NXDOMAIN Ratio'. If NXDOMAIN TLD Concentration hits > 80%, the malware is hyper-focusing its failed guesses on a specific Top Level Domain (like `.ru` or `.cc`)."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 311,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "New Domains (DGA Burst)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 85, "w": 8, "h": 8},
      "targets": [{"expr": "home_ids_new_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}", "refId": "A"}]
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Suspicious / DGA Domains",
      "gridPos": {"x": 8, "y": 85, "w": 8, "h": 8},
      "targets": [{"expr": "home_ids_suspicious_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}", "refId": "A"}],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
